General.Name: Zhuhai Winbase International Chemical Tank Terminal Co Ltd
General.Description: Zhuhai Winbase International Chemical Tank Terminal Co.,Ltd engages in the terminal loading and unloading, warehousing, barge transfer, and pipeline transportation and bonded activities for bulk liquid petrochemicals in China. Zhuhai Winbase International Chemical Tank Terminal Co.,Ltd was founded in 2000 and is based in Zhuhai, China.
General.Address: Nanjingwan Petrochemical Storage Zone, Zhuhai, China
